info.author: Philippe Dalet
info.description:
TDS2xx is a Tektronix oscilloscope family with GPIB and SERIAL port.
This module is connected with the 82357A USB-GPIB running
only on windows (XP pro,W2K,Me,W98) or with a serial cable.

- Connect 82357A on USB port
- Install agilent driver (see CDROM IO libraries for instrument control
  Revision: L.02.00)
- Install 82357A  python package.
- Install this python package TDS200.

OR

- Connect the cable on the serial port 
- Install pyserial python package.
- Install this python package TDS200.
